eel comfortable, and over time built a loyal client base rooted in trust, experience, and friendship.\n<br><br>\nAfter years behind the massage table, I’m aligning my business with expansion and elevation. Now, I’m leaning into education, mentorship, and product development. I’m at a point in my life where I want to service clients because I have passion for waxing, not solely for income. It feels amazing to create space to inspire and teach other waxers to confidently grow, scale, and build with purpose.","columns_desktop":2,"rows_desktop":2,"columns_mobile":1,"rows_mobile":3,"grid_gap_desktop":20,"grid_gap_mobile":16,"cell_padding_desktop":10,"cell_padding_mobile":8,"icon_gap_desktop":12,"icon_gap_mobile":10,"main_link_margin":10,"button_bg":"#000000","button_text":"#ffffff","icon_size_desktop":48,"icon_size_mobile":64,"video_bg":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/kyana-bailey-3.jpg","section_video_url":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/videos\/c\/o\/v\/79903f7f1f834a8e9608e04030891d73.mp4","margin_top":"","margin_bottom":""}},"about_introduce":{"type":"about-introduce","blocks":{"a653e752-d2e2-4d29-b960-f964706f33f1":{"type":"introduce","settings":{"image_intro":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/jazminborgesimmortalbeauty.png","title_intro":"Jazmin Borges","des_intro":"Advanced Educator Ambassador","content_intro":"My mission with Immortal Beauty Co is to help share my experience on making every guest feel beautiful, seen, safe and respected. <br><br>I aim to inspire confidence in other beauty professionals, driven by the belief of equality and the passion to help others feel they have a space to be serviced and heard."}}},"block_order":["a653e752-d2e2-4d29-b960-f964706f33f1"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"enable_intro":true}},"section_collection_v1_MeH3QT":{"type":"section-collection-v1","blocks":{"collection_UCgEtx":{"type":"collection","settings":{"bg_color":"#ffffff","img_collection":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/1_b7d07b6e-0eea-4e87-96fa-6a5330cea17b.png","block_title":"Brazilian Wax<br>Advanced Training - May 9th","color_title":"","block_des":"Learn Brazilian waxing with 3-4 models provided for hands on learning. Class runs from 9am-3\/4pm. To book, contact Jazmin via email or text to receive your class contract and complete payment. Cost $750, lunch included.\n<br><br>\nClasses are held at:\n<br><br>\nImmortal Beauty Co\n<br>\n1016 East Main Road\n<br>\nPortsmouth, RI 02871","color_des":"","block_buton":"Book a Seat!","block_url":"shopify:\/\/products\/brazilian-wax-classes-w-jazmin-borges-portsmouth-rhode-island","effect_heading":"fadeInUp","effect_duration_heading":"1s","effect_delay_heading":"0s","effect_desc":"fadeInUp","effect_duration_desc":"1s","effect_delay_desc":"0s","effect_sub_heading":"fadeInUp","effect_duration_sub_heading":"1s","effect_delay_sub_heading":"0s"}}},"block_order":["collection_UCgEtx"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"margin_top":"","margin_bottom":"","button_bg_color":"#e272a3","button_hover_color":"#333333","button_font_color":"#ffffff","button_hover_font_color":"#ffffff"}},"bombshell_50_means_6KB64U":{"type":"bombshell-50-means","name":"What It Means Bombshell 50","settings":{"show_eyebrow":true,"eyebrow_text":"","heading":"<p>What it means to me to be a <em>Bombshell<\/em><\/p>","heading_tag":"h2","show_quote_mark":true,"quote_text":"Being an Official Bombshell means proving to myself that this business is bigger than just me - it’s about impact. It’s about influencing with intention and building something that inspires you inside the treatment room and beyond. I’m thrilled to be titled California Bombshell!","esthetician_name":"Kyana","esthetician_title":"","badge_text":"","meta_state":"","meta_member_since":"2022","meta_specialty":"","background_color":"#FFFFFF","heading_color":"#111111","quote_text_color":"#111111","gold_color":"#e272a3","meta_text_color":"#111111","padding_top":64,"padding_bottom":64}},"about_servicebox":{"type":"about-servicebox","blocks":{"15e208a6-b518-4d9e-8f27-0bd7642f7b52":{"type":"service","